OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fa few light showers possible during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Largely dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells developing overnight, although
OL,9,Fwith a few isolated coastal showers
OL,10,Flikely. Feeling cool with a brisk
OL,11,Fnortherly wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FSunny spells for many,
OL,14,Fthough cooler than recent days.
OL,15,FLargely dry to the west, with
OL,16,Foccasional showers affecting East
OL,17,FAnglia. Breezy, especially along
OL,18,Fcoasts. Chilly overnight with frosts
OL,19,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
